This package redistributes, under the `rules/` directory, the AI-DLC rule
bundle from the awslabs/aidlc-workflows project as an offline fallback:

  awslabs/aidlc-workflows
  https://github.com/awslabs/aidlc-workflows
  Licensed under the MIT-0 License.

The vendored rule files (rules/aws-aidlc-rules/ and rules/aws-aidlc-rule-details/)
are unmodified copies pinned to release v0.1.8. At install time, `opencode-aidlc
setup` prefers downloading the latest release directly from the upstream project
and only uses this vendored copy when the download is unavailable.
